<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Solbakken Research Initiative</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400&family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

:root {
–bg: #0a0c0f;
–surface: #111318;
–border: #1e2229;
–accent: #c8a96e;
–accent-dim: #7a6340;
–text: #d4cfc8;
–text-dim: #6b6660;
–text-bright: #ede8e0;
–mono: ‘DM Mono’, monospace;
–serif: ‘Playfair Display’, serif;
–body: ‘Cormorant Garamond’, serif;
}

body {
background: var(–bg);
color: var(–text);
font-family: var(–body);
font-size: 17px;
line-height: 1.75;
min-height: 100vh;
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
}

header {
border-bottom: 1px solid var(–border);
padding: 3.5rem 2.5rem 3rem;
max-width: 860px;
margin: 0 auto;
width: 100%;
}

.org-label {
font-family: var(–mono);
font-size: 0.62rem;
letter-spacing: 0.22em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(–accent);
margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
}

h1 {
font-family: var(–serif);
font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
font-weight: 700;
color: var(–text-bright);
line-height: 1.15;
margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.org-desc {
font-family: var(–body);
font-size: 1rem;
color: var(–text-dim);
max-width: 520px;
line-height: 1.7;
}

main {
max-width: 860px;
margin: 0 auto;
padding: 3rem 2.5rem 6rem;
width: 100%;
flex: 1;
}

.section-label {
font-family: var(–mono);
font-size: 0.62rem;
letter-spacing: 0.2em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(–accent-dim);
margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 0.8rem;
}

.section-label::after {
content: ‘’;
flex: 1;
height: 1px;
background: var(–border);
}

/* PAPER CARD */
.paper-card {
display: block;
text-decoration: none;
border: 1px solid var(–border);
padding: 2rem 2.2rem;
background: var(–surface);
transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
position: relative;
}

.paper-card:hover {
border-color: var(–accent-dim);
}

.paper-card:hover .paper-arrow {
transform: translateX(4px);
color: var(–accent);
}

.paper-meta {
font-family: var(–mono);
font-size: 0.62rem;
letter-spacing: 0.12em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(–text-dim);
margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
display: flex;
gap: 1.2rem;
}

.paper-meta .status {
color: var(–accent-dim);
}

.paper-title {
font-family: var(–serif);
font-size: 1.45rem;
font-weight: 700;
color: var(–text-bright);
line-height: 1.2;
margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}

.paper-subtitle {
font-family: var(–serif);
font-style: italic;
font-size: 0.95rem;
color: var(–text-dim);
margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
}

.paper-abstract {
font-size: 0.9rem;
color: var(–text);
line-height: 1.7;
margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
max-width: 600px;
}

.paper-tags {
display: flex;
gap: 0.5rem;
flex-wrap: wrap;
margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
}

.tag {
font-family: var(–mono);
font-size: 0.58rem;
letter-spacing: 0.1em;
text-transform: uppercase;
padding: 0.22rem 0.6rem;
border: 1px solid var(–border);
color: var(–text-dim);
}

.paper-arrow {
font-family: var(–mono);
font-size: 0.72rem;
color: var(–accent-dim);
letter-spacing: 0.05em;
transition: transform 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
display: inline-block;
}

/* FOOTER */
footer {
border-top: 1px solid var(–border);
padding: 1.8rem 2.5rem;
max-width: 860px;
margin: 0 auto;
width: 100%;
font-family: var(–mono);
font-size: 0.6rem;
letter-spacing: 0.1em;
color: var(–text-dim);
display: flex;
justify-content: space-between;
flex-wrap: wrap;
gap: 0.5rem;
}

@keyframes fadeUp {
from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(14px); }
to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

header { animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease both; }
main   { animation: fadeUp 0.5s 0.08s ease both; }
</style>

</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="org-label">Solbakken Research Initiative</div>
  <h1>Independent Research in<br>Photonic &amp; Materials Computing</h1>
  <p class="org-desc">Speculative and pre-experimental frameworks for next-generation compute substrates, photonic AI acceleration, and orbital manufacturing. Independent. Pre-institutional.</p>
</header>

<main>

  <div class="section-label">Publications &amp; Working Papers</div>

  <a class="paper-card" href="carbon-from-above.html">
    <div class="paper-meta">
      <span>March 2026</span>
      <span class="status">Speculative · Pre-Experimental</span>
      <span>Version 5</span>
    </div>
    <div class="paper-title">Carbon From Above</div>
    <div class="paper-subtitle">Orbital Diamond Fabrication from Asteroid Carbon Feedstock</div>
    <p class="paper-abstract">A closed-loop orbital supply chain converting ureilite asteroid carbon into CVD-grown diamond substrates via concentrated solar power. Addresses silicon's radiation vulnerability for orbital AI compute through a three-phase development pathway from 2026 to 2050.</p>
    <div class="paper-tags">
      <span class="tag">Diamond CVD</span>
      <span class="tag">ISRU</span>
      <span class="tag">Orbital Solar</span>
      <span class="tag">Radiation Hardness</span>
      <span class="tag">Photonic Compute</span>
    </div>
    <span class="paper-arrow">Read paper →</span>
  </a>

</main>

<footer>
  <span>Solbakken Research Initiative</span>
  <span>Independent · Unaffiliated · Open</span>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
